  <summary>2/16/2000--Introduced.
Partial Birth Abortion and Judicial Limitation Act of 2000 - Amends the Federal judicial code to provide that neither the Federal district courts nor the United States Court of Federal Claims shall have jurisdiction to hear or determine any partial-birth abortion-related case.</summary>
